    "description": "Flibbles is a third person casual adventure, placing you in the marvelous world of Flibble Land. You are farmer going about your daily routine, when suddenly you are faced up against a mysterious foe only known as Purple Goo. Its up to you fend off the Purple Goo and save Flibble Land and its cute and adorable creatures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Flibbles!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/1e7c6110eb99ef699e50e6d28ad501b6.poster.avif?t=1639262515\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/1e7c6110eb99ef699e50e6d28ad501b6.webm?t=1639262515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/1e7c6110eb99ef699e50e6d28ad501b6.mp4?t=1639262515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Variety of Flibbles to collect, each with a unique appearance and abilities. Tame Flibbles along your journey and command them to your will.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Avatar Customization!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/6650a271356043711cb3f845eb6c1d39.poster.avif?t=1639262515\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/6650a271356043711cb3f845eb6c1d39.webm?t=1639262515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/6650a271356043711cb3f845eb6c1d39.mp4?t=1639262515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Customize your avatar with your surroundings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Crafting!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/111b04ecc5218c29d629536af999a5d9.poster.avif?t=1639262515\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/111b04ecc5218c29d629536af999a5d9.webm?t=1639262515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/111b04ecc5218c29d629536af999a5d9.mp4?t=1639262515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Combine objects around you and create the necessary items at hand.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fishing!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/57e42983590c9f019d26dd30b952382f.poster.avif?t=1639262515\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/57e42983590c9f019d26dd30b952382f.webm?t=1639262515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744820/extras/57e42983590c9f019d26dd30b952382f.mp4?t=1639262515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fish for a chance to tame new and unique Flibbles to add to your collection.",
